<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Rest-Client on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/rest-client/</link><description>Recent content in Rest-Client on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/rest-client/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Elasticsearch ResponseException — ES REST Client Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/elasticsearch-rest/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/elasticsearch-rest/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="elasticsearch-responseexception--es-rest-client-fix"&gt;Elasticsearch ResponseException — ES REST Client Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ResponseException&lt;/code&gt; from the Elasticsearch REST client is thrown when the client receives an error response from Elasticsearch. This includes connection failures, mapping errors, and query errors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common message:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ResponseException: method [GET], host [localhost:9200], URI [/my-index/_search]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ResponseException: [mapper_parsing_exception]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Index does not exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;RestHighLevelClient client &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; ...;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;client.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; GetRequest(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;nonexistent-index&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;), RequestOptions.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DEFAULT&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Mapping error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Field type mismatch in indexing request&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Connection refused&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Elasticsearch not running on localhost:9200&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-create-index-first"&gt;Fix 1: Create index first&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;CreateIndexRequest request &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; CreateIndexRequest(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;my-index&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;client.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;indices&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt;(request, RequestOptions.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DEFAULT&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-check-elasticsearch-connectivity"&gt;Fix 2: Check Elasticsearch connectivity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl -v http://localhost:9200/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl http://localhost:9200/_cluster/health
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-handle-errors-gracefully"&gt;Fix 3: Handle errors gracefully&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; GetResponse response &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; client.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; GetRequest(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;my-index&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;), RequestOptions.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DEFAULT&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (ResponseException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getResponse&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getStatusLine&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getStatusCode&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; 404) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Handle not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-correct-mapping"&gt;Fix 4: Use correct mapping&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;XContentBuilder mapping &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; XContentFactory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;jsonBuilder&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;startObject&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;startObject&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;properties&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;startObject&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;field&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;text&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;endObject&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;startObject&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;email&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;field&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keyword&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;endObject&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;endObject&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;endObject&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/spring-data-elasticsearch/ — Spring Data Elasticsearch errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/testcontainers-elasticsearch/ — ElasticsearchContainer startup failed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Elasticsearch REST High-Level Client Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/elasticsearch-rest-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/elasticsearch-rest-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="elasticsearch-rest-high-level-client-error-fix"&gt;Elasticsearch REST High-Level Client Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An Elasticsearch REST high-level client error occurs when the Java client fails to communicate with the Elasticsearch cluster or encounters mapping/index issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ResponseException: method [POST], host [localhost], URI [/myindex/_search]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ElasticsearchStatusException: Elasticsearch exception [mapper_parsing_exception]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ConnectException: Connect to localhost:9200 failed&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ResponseException: all shards failed&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The high-level REST client encountered an error during index, search, or mapping operations. This can indicate connectivity issues, mapping problems, or Elasticsearch version incompatibility.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] ResourceAccessException Timeout — Spring REST Client Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/spring-rest-client/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/spring-rest-client/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="resourceaccessexception-timeout--spring-rest-client-fix"&gt;ResourceAccessException Timeout — Spring REST Client Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ResourceAccessException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a Spring REST client (RestTemplate or WebClient) cannot complete a request due to connection or read timeout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common message:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ResourceAccessException: I/O error on GET request&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: No timeout configured&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;RestTemplate restTemplate &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; RestTemplate();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Default timeout too low for slow services&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Connection pool exhaustion&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-configure-resttemplate-timeouts"&gt;Fix 1: Configure RestTemplate timeouts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Bean&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; RestTemplate &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;restTemplate&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory factory &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setConnectTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(5000);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setReadTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(10000);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; RestTemplate(factory);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-configure-webclient-timeouts"&gt;Fix 2: Configure WebClient timeouts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Bean&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; WebClient &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;webClient&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; HttpClient httpClient &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; HttpClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;option&lt;/span&gt;(ChannelOption.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;CONNECT_TIMEOUT_MILLIS&lt;/span&gt;, 5000)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;responseTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(10));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; WebClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;builder&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;clientConnector&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ReactClientHttpConnector(httpClient))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;build&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/resttemplate-timeout/ — ResourceAccessException timeout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/webclient-timeout/ — WebClientRequestException timeout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/languages/java/resttemplate/ — RestClientResponseException&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>HttpClientErrorException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/http-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/http-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Spring&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;RestTemplate&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;WebClient&lt;/code&gt; receives a 4xx response from an external API. The default behavior is to throw an exception instead of returning the response.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External API returned 400 Bad Request (invalid input)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Authentication failed (401 Unauthorized)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Insufficient permissions (403 Forbidden)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resource not found (404 Not Found)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle 4xx responses with error handling:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ResponseEntity&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;User&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; response &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; restTemplate.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exchange&lt;/span&gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;https://api.example.com/users/{id}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; HttpMethod.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;GET&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; User.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; userId
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; );
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; response.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getBody&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (HttpClientErrorException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getStatusCode&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; HttpStatus.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;NOT_FOUND&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ResourceNotFoundException(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;User not found&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; e;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;RestTemplate&lt;/code&gt; with custom error handler:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;restTemplate.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setErrorHandler&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ResponseErrorHandler() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Override&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hasError&lt;/span&gt;(ClientHttpResponse response) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; response.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getStatusCode&lt;/span&gt;().&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;is4xxClientError&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Override&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;handleError&lt;/span&gt;(ClientHttpResponse response) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Custom error handling logic&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;WebClient&lt;/code&gt; for non-blocking requests with error handling:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;webClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;uri&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/users/{id}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, userId)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;retrieve&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;onStatus&lt;/span&gt;(HttpStatusCode::is4xxClientError, response &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; response.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;bodyToMono&lt;/span&gt;(String.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;flatMap&lt;/span&gt;(body &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; Mono.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ResourceNotFoundException(body)));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; })
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;bodyToMono&lt;/span&gt;(User.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 404 from external API&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; restTemplate.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getForObject&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;https://api.example.com/users/999&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, User.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (HttpClientErrorException.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;NotFound&lt;/span&gt; e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;User not found: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getResponseBodyAsString&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;HttpClientErrorException$NotFound: 404 Not Found: {&amp;#34;error&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;User not found&amp;#34;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/transaction-error/"&gt;Transaction error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ResourceAccessException - REST client timeout</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-rest-client-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-rest-client-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Spring&amp;rsquo;s REST client (RestTemplate, WebClient, RestClient) encounters a connection failure or timeout while making an HTTP request. It throws &lt;code&gt;ResourceAccessException&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Target service is unreachable or down&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connection timeout configured too aggressively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DNS resolution failure for the target host&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SSL/TLS handshake failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network proxy blocking the connection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure timeouts for RestTemplate:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Bean&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; RestTemplate &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;restTemplate&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory factory &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setConnectTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(5));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setReadTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(10));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; RestTemplate(factory);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure timeouts for WebClient:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Bean&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; WebClient &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;webClient&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; HttpClient httpClient &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; HttpClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;responseTimeout&lt;/span&gt;(Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(10))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;option&lt;/span&gt;(ChannelOption.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;CONNECT_TIMEOUT_MILLIS&lt;/span&gt;, 5000);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; WebClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;builder&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;clientConnector&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ReactorClientHttpConnector(httpClient))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;build&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add retry logic for transient failures:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ExternalApiService&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; WebClient webClient;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; Mono&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;ExternalResponse&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;callExternalApi&lt;/span&gt;(String id) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; webClient.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;uri&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/api/external/{id}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, id)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;retrieve&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;bodyToMono&lt;/span&gt;(ExternalResponse.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;timeout&lt;/span&gt;(Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(5))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;retryWhen&lt;/span&gt;(Retry.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;backoff&lt;/span&gt;(3, Duration.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ofSeconds&lt;/span&gt;(1))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;filter&lt;/span&gt;(throwable &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; throwable &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; ResourceAccessException));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;restTemplate.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getForObject&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;http://down-service/api/data&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, String.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ResourceAccessException: I/O error on GET http://down-service/api/data&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-cloud-gateway-error/"&gt;Gateway error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-retry-error/"&gt;Retry error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>